There is some issue with this design
1. Notification service have all the responsibility to handle notification for push notification, SMS and email notification
2. If multiple service are sending the notification , then in that case , service may be not able to handle the load and notofication start dropping off
3. Notification service becomes SPOF ,
4. there will be challenge to scale service
5. if we are using rate limit and authentication , then we have to put all those in same service , which is unrequired task for core service (Mostly service which handle the business)
